snippet.title: Crazy Shipping Trailer
snippet.description:
Crazy Shipping is a free-to-play space transport management game where your fleet of felines deliver anything, anywhere - no questions asked. In space, no one can hear you scheme!

Check out Crazy Shipping on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3254840/Crazy_Shipping/
